，川瀨萌綁著可愛包頭，身穿綠色長版外衣，「中路大開」的穿搭秀出紅色內衣包覆下的柔美胸型，兼具性感與可愛。<br />\n<br />\n目前25歲的川瀨萌，擁有中日混血身分，是以「遊戲實況主」打響知名度。去年12月份，出版了生涯首冊寫真集，獲得不少粉絲支持。寫真集封面更以「最美姐姐的的正統後繼者」一語做為形容。<br />\n<br />\n除了大秀性感之外，川瀨萌的IG也有許多清純系美圖，有眼尖網友就認為，她的外貌與新垣結衣有幾分相似，而她更加升級的胸圍，更讓粉絲半開玩笑地說「這是結衣2.0」。"},{"pid":"ab77c409938fd86ebcdf58b406483ca4d7a6c0cc","tid":2070074,"uid":61207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T03:06:03.000Z","msg":"又p圖又露晒底<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4a9d3c6a63a170c575b8a6cd6c8843f874ed3ad","tid":2070074,"uid":75100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T03:27:05.000Z","msg":"哇屌你老母欺詐既，上youtube搵左段片見到真身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b9ea08045c73debc6eb59d14fba972aed445628","tid":2070074,"uid":176246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T03:37:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港SIZE C囉<br />\n波型都唔靚 可以收返埋"}]}